### ============================================================
### query-burst-msa catalog-service API
### Base URL: http://localhost:18113
### ============================================================

# @no-log

### Health
GET http://localhost:18113/actuator/health

### ============================================================
### [DATA INIT]
### ============================================================

### 테스트 데이터 적재 시작
POST http://localhost:18113/api/data-init

### 테스트 데이터 적재 상태 확인
GET http://localhost:18113/api/data-init/status

### ============================================================
### [CATEGORY]
### ============================================================

### 카테고리 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:18113/api/categories

### 루트 카테고리 생성
POST http://localhost:18113/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "전자제품",
  "parentId": null
}

### 하위 카테고리 생성
POST http://localhost:18113/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "노트북",
  "parentId": 1
}

### 카테고리 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:18113/api/categories/1

### ============================================================
### [PRODUCT]
### ============================================================

### 상품 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:18113/api/products?size=20

### 상품 목록 조회 - 카테고리 필터
GET http://localhost:18113/api/products?categoryId=1&size=20

### 상품 목록 조회 - 상태 필터
GET http://localhost:18113/api/products?status=ACTIVE&size=20

### 상품 목록 조회 - 다음 페이지
GET http://localhost:18113/api/products?cursor=1000&size=20

### 상품 생성
POST http://localhost:18113/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "맥북 프로",
  "price": 3200000,
  "stock": 50,
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "sellerId": 1
}

### 상품 가격 수정
PATCH http://localhost:18113/api/products/1/price?price=2990000

### 상품 상태 변경
PATCH http://localhost:18113/api/products/1/status?status=SOLD_OUT

### 상품 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:18113/api/products/1

### ============================================================
### [INVENTORY]
### ============================================================

### 재고 예약
POST http://localhost:18113/internal/inventory/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requestId": "catalog-reserve-demo-1",
  "orderId": 900001,
  "memberId": 1001,
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

### 재고 예약 확정
POST http://localhost:18113/internal/inventory/reservations/1/commit

### 재고 예약 해제
POST http://localhost:18113/internal/inventory/reservations/1/release
